headline: Generac Holdings Stock Outlook: Is Wall Street Bullish or Bearish?
summary: Despite Generac Holdings’ outperformance relative to the broader market over the past year, Wall Street analysts maintain a cautiously optimistic outlook on the stock’s prospects.
